’Щ@410b11c3621012cd8b68c335725328143504ac23e2f26454a695ea250941b24cЪ7Title: title: into duration
Path: Examples
Content:
Convert duration string to duration value.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '7min' | into duration
7min

```
Convert compound duration string to duration value.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1day 2hr 3min 4sec' | into duration
1day 2hr 3min 4sec

```
Convert table of duration strings to table of duration values.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[value]; ['1sec'] ['2min'] ['3hr'] ['4day'] ['5wk']] | into duration value
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ value в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ  1sec в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ  2min в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ   3hr в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3 в”Ӯ  4day в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4 в”Ӯ   5wk в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Convert duration to duration.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 420sec | into duration
7min

```
Convert 
``hh:mm:ss``
-style string to duration
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '3:34:00' | into duration
3hr 34min

```
Convert 
``hh:mm:ss.f``
-style string to duration
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '2:45:31.2' | into duration
2hr 45min 31sec 200ms

```
Convert a number of ns to duration.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1_234_567 | into duration
1ms 234Вөs 567ns

```
Convert a number of an arbitrary unit to duration.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1_234 | into duration --unit ms
1sec 234ms

```
Convert a floating point number of an arbitrary unit to duration.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1.234 | into duration --unit sec
1sec 234ms

```
Convert a record to a duration.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> {day: 10, hour: 2, minute: 6, second: 50, sign: '+'} | into duration
1wk 3day 2hr 6min 50sec

```
’Щ@df51ed9f765716c646a26e374cce39542ae06ed35f984b1a294e4f06e4ddddd8ЩғTitle: title: into duration
Path: Notes
Content:
Max duration value is i64::MAX nanoseconds; max duration time unit is wk (weeks).
